Task: Household Energy Consumption Forecasting (Time Series)
Objective: Resample and forecast hourly energy usage to predict future demand and reduce noise in high-frequency power data.

Key Skills: Time Series Analysis, ARIMA Modeling, Data Resampling.

Technical Challenges Overcome: Resolved a ValueError caused by deprecated pandas frequency aliases (updating 'H' to 'h') and handled non-numeric noise (characters like '?') in the raw dataset.

Outcome: A predictive model that identifies daily energy trends, allowing for better load balancing and efficiency analysis.
